Ranger Help for: make
=====================

SUMMARY:
The unified crafting command. Rangers can craft all their gear from
natural materials found in the wild.

USAGE:
  make                  Show all available items
  make rope             Twist grasses into rope
  make torch            Carve a wooden torch
  make fish trap        Weave a trap for catching camp fish
  make tent             Build a tent from rope and wood
  make tools            Prepare a reusable field kit
  make satchel          Expand your wildcraft forage pouch
  make arrow            Carve arrows from wood
  make bolt             Carve crossbow bolts from wood
  make bow              Carve a shortbow from wood
  make crossbow         Carve a crossbow from wood
  make longbow          Carve a longbow from wood
  make trophy           Mount a trophy from a corpse
  make snare <dir>      Set a snare trap in a direction

REQUIREMENTS:
All crafting requires a slash weapon (knife/sword) equipped. Most
items need specific terrain or materials:

  rope         Grass terrain (forest, plains, swamp)
  torch        Wood terrain (forest, jungle, swamp, mountain)
  fish trap    2 binding fiber + 1 kindling
  tent         Wood terrain + rope in inventory
  tools        2 fieldstone + 1 flint + 1 binding fiber
  satchel      3 hide scraps + 2 sinew + 2 binding fiber
  arrow/bolt   Wood terrain (quantity based on skill)
  bow types    Wood terrain + 2 wood (10 sec delay)
  trophy       Corpse in the room
  snare        Rope in inventory + valid exit direction

CRAFTING CHAINS:
  make rope -> make tent -> camp (set up a wilderness camp)
  mine/quarry + forage -> make tools -> mine more reliably
  skin corpse + forage -> make satchel
  forage + make fish trap -> set fish trap -> camp cook
  make arrow + make bow -> archery combat
  make bolt + make crossbow -> heartshot

If your wildcraft pouch fills with the wrong supplies, use
'forage stores' to review it and 'forage discard <component> [amount]'
to free room. Camp stock, camp cook, and camp brew also consume
wildcraft supplies.

